name: DBL - Extra Viejo Double Prensado - Toro
additionalNotes: The DBL Extra Viejo is an exquisite cigar that turns heads and demands respect. Its beautiful Mexican Arapiraca wrapper is smooth and silky with a dark, oily sheen. The binder is Dominican and the filler is Dominican and Brazilian. It is a medium-full strength cigar that packs plenty of rich, savory flavors that are sure to impress. The Extra Viejo is presented in a breathtaking humidor loaded with 41 total cigars in three sizes (toro, robusto, gordo).
